title: Design House Wyndham 19x17 One Door Cultured Marble Vanity Top, Unassembled, 4-Inch Centerset
features: This bathroom vanity cabinet ships to your home flat in protected packaging and ready to assemble. Step-by-step instructions are provided and all parts are labeled to make assembly easier
Frameless design for increased storage space
3 pre-drilled holes allow for a 4-inch center mount faucet while the overflow hole and integrated backsplash prevent water damage
Assembled: 19 in. W x 17 in. D x 34.19 in. H, Base: 18 in. W x 15.75 in. D x 31.5 in. H, Top: 19 in. W x 17 in. D x 2.69 in. H
description: The Design House 19-inch Wyndham bathroom vanity set makes an elegant storage solution for any country style home. Timeless simplicity at its best, this piece presents clean lines for a classic look and a durable white semi-gloss finish with satin nickel knobs for easy access. Features include a 1-door construction with a frameless design for enhanced storage space, keeping your toiletries tucked away and countertop free of clutter. The Wyndham vanity is stylishly paired with a stunning white on white cultured marble top, creating a classic, united look with the crisp white base and providing long-lasting durability for years to come. One overflow hole and three 4-inch straight holes are pre-drilled atop an oval bowl to install your faucet and an integrated backsplash helps prevents water damage. This countertop's squared edges add a modern design to appeal to contemporary tastes. The vanity base comes unassembled. The Design House 19-inch Wyndham bathroom vanity set has a 1-year limited warranty that protects against defects in materials and workmanship. Designed and manufactured by Design House, the trusted source for quality lighting, hardware, plumbing, kitchen, and bath products for every taste and budget.
